Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.util

Class LinkedListTest

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.util.LinkedListTest
public class LinkedListTest extends Object
Test class for the custom LinkedList implementation. This class performs unit tests to verify the behavior of the LinkedList class and its methods, including add, remove, set, contains, size, and ListIterator functionalities. The tests include scenarios for valid and invalid inputs, boundary conditions, and edge cases. It uses the JUnit testing framework to assert expected outcomes.
